,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"AI Agent 登录流程：\n1. 执行 `x hub login`\n2. 读取输出中的 URL=xxx\n3. 将 URL 发送给用户，让用户在浏览器中打开并完成授权（无需用户回复已授权，程序会自动轮询检测）\n4. 等待输出 STATUS=success 即表示登录成功\n"
,
"en"
:
"AI Agent login flow:\n1. Execute `x hub login`\n2. Read the URL=xxx from the output\n3. Send the URL to the user, ask them to open it in a browser and complete authorization (no need for the user to confirm, the program polls automatically)\n4. Wait for STATUS=success in the output, which means login succeeded\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub login"
,
"cn"
:
"登录/注册账户，AI Agent 直接运行即可"
,
"en"
:
"Login/register account, AI agents can run this directly"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub login github"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 GitHub 登录"
,
"en"
:
"Login with GitHub"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub login email <email>"
,
"cn"
:
"使用邮箱登录"
,
"en"
:
"Login with email"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub login --expire <duration> wechat"
,
"cn"
:
"微信登录，指定过期时间（如 1d、7d）"
,
"en"
:
"Login with WeChat, set expiration (e.g., 1d, 7d)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub login --expire <duration> --region <region> email <email>"
,
"cn"
:
"邮箱登录，指定过期时间和地区"
,
"en"
:
"Email login with custom expiration and region"
}
]
}

